+   sp+32 (with the int at sp+16).
+**bar:
+**	...
+**	ldr	w[0-9]+, \[x[0-9]+, 16\]
+**	ldr	q0, \[x[0-9]+\]
+**	...
+**	ldr	q1, \[x[0-9]+, 32\]
+**	bl	___addtf3
+**	...
+*/
+
